# ================================================================
# CRITICAL DEPLOYMENT FILES
# ================================================================
# Package lock files are essential for repeatable, secure deployments.
# The '!' prefix ensures they are NEVER ignored, even if a parent
# directory or a wildcard rule tries to exclude them.
# THIS IS THE FIX FOR THE DEPLOYMENT ERROR.
!package-lock.json
!pnpm-lock.yaml
!yarn.lock